name: Sil Unch
Lore: 'Neimoidian Trade Federation Droid Control Ship officer. Specialized in battle droid control programming and interfaces. Does not enjoy being commanded by Daultay Dofine.',
Text: 'Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. While aboard a battleship, that battleship is immune to attrition < 4 and draws a battle destiny if not able to otherwise.',
